name: Lara
description: I would say that I am a very down to earth Woman, someone who enjoys life and tries to live it the best I can. I enjoy the simple things, that life offers rather then being caught up into all the craziness one can experience. I love the outdoors especially the beach, catching a sunset then taking in the sounds of the crashing waves it can be so soothing. I have learned to appreciate the simple things, in life and not take people or things for granted. Instead I appreciate who they are and what they have done to make me a better person.
